subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description:
Project outputs: 
- to improve cross border cooperation, the capacity to reduce crime and improve legal trade, travel and commerce along Afghanistan’s border with Tajikistan and Uzbekistan. 
- to contribute to mutual trust, regional development, conflict resolution and prevention, and enhanced human security, as well as to indirectly enhance and expand economic development on both sides of the border.
subproject.title: Border Mngment in North Afghan
